94
00:04:10,042 --> 00:04:11,710
Stand up tall, okay?

95
00:04:12,044 --> 00:04:14,546
Your old self has disappeared.

96
00:04:14,613 --> 00:04:16,615
As you navigate your thirties
and approach your forties

97
00:04:16,982 --> 00:04:19,184
