the affection you get back.

117
00:05:19,044 --> 00:05:20,078
It breaks my heart.

118
00:05:20,646 --> 00:05:21,814
It saddens me.

119
00:05:23,048 --> 00:05:24,316
You pitiful thing.

120
00:05:24,783 --> 00:05:25,784
What's more

121
