1768
01:10:11,598 --> 01:10:13,300
GUGI-DONG FAM'S HOUSE SQUAD GOAL

1769
01:10:13,367 --> 01:10:15,102
BRINGING BACK THE GAMES
OF THEIR CHILDHOOD

1770
01:10:15,169 --> 01:10:17,538
Do you know the difference
