1780
01:10:40,461 --> 01:10:42,029
- P!nk.
- Is it really?

1781
01:10:42,363 --> 01:10:44,131
This brings me back.

1782
01:10:44,198 --> 01:10:45,833
- It brings back so many memories.
- This song...

1783
01:10:45,899 --> 01:10:48,002
